author: The Associated Press
title: China to end lockdown of most of virus-hit Hubei province at midnight; restrictions on Wuhan to remain until April 8
description: China to end lockdown of most of virus-hit Hubei province at midnight; restrictions on Wuhan to remain until April 8
content:
BEIJING -- 
China to end lockdown of most of virus-hit Hubei province at midnight; restrictions on Wuhan to remain until April 8.
